devdoc.details: Can be used without organization just as a vesting component.

collect(uint256).details: Function for a beneficiary to collect.

params._params: array _params[0] _startingBlock the block from which the agreement starts. _params[1] _amountPerPeriod amount of tokens per period. _params[2] _periodLength period length in blocks. _params[3] _numOfAgreedPeriods how many periods agreed on. _params[4] _cliffInPeriods the length of the cliff in periods. _params[5] _signaturesReqToCancel number of signatures required to cancel agreement.
params._returnOnCancelAddress: where to send the tokens in case of stoping.
params._signersArray: avatar array of addresses that can sign to cancel agreement.
params._token: the relevant token in the agreement.

executeProposal(bytes32,int256).details: execution of proposals, can only be called by the voting machine in which the vote is held.

params._param: a parameter of the voting result, 1 yes and 2 is no.
params._proposalId: the ID of the voting in the voting machine

executeProposal(bytes32,int256).return: bool which represents a successful of the function

getParametersHash(bytes32,address).details: Hash the parameters, and return the hash value

isOwner().return: true if `msg.sender` is the owner of the contract.

proposeVestingAgreement(address,address,.details: Proposing a vesting agreement in an organization.

params._cliffInPeriods: the length of the cliff in periods.
params._returnOnCancelAddress: where to send the tokens in case of stoping.
params._signaturesReqToCancel: number of signatures required to cancel agreement.
params._signersArray: avatar array of addresses that can sign to cancel agreement.
params._startingBlock: the block from which the agreement starts.

renounceOwnership().details: Allows the current owner to relinquish control of the contract.

revokeSignToCancelAgreement(uint256).details: Function to revoke vote for canceling agreement.

setParameters(bytes32,address).details: Hash the parameters, save them if necessary, and return the hash value

signToCancelAgreement(uint256).details: Function to sign to cancel an agreement.

transferOwnership(address).details: Allows the current owner to transfer control of the contract to a newOwner.

params.newOwner: The address to transfer ownership to.

devdoc.title: A scheme for vesting.

renounceOwnership().notice: Renouncing to ownership will leave the contract without an owner. It will not be possible to call the functions with the `onlyOwner` modifier anymore.
